      "text": "# Rotterdam SafeRoute AI safety and Helpline Guide This guide compiles essential emergency numbers, Dutch legal rights regarding harassment, and safety resources for Rotterdam. ## Emergency Contact Numbers - **Immediate Life Threat / Active Crime (Police/Fire/Ambulance):** Dial **112** (24/7, free of charge). - **Non-Emergency Police Support:** Dial **0900-8844** (for reporting suspicious activity or non-violent past incidents). - **Veilig Thuis (Domestic Abuse & Harassment Helpline):** Dial **0800-2000** (24/7 free hotline for safety advice and reporting stalking). - **Rotterdam Women's Safe Haven Shelter (NGO):** Call **+31 10 476 1234** (provides emergency shelter, crisis support, and legal guidance). - **Slachtofferhulp Nederland (Victim Support):** Dial **0900-0101** (confidential emotional and legal guidance for victims of harassment or assault). ## Dutch Street Harassment Laws - **Street",
